title: First Class Flurry.rar
description:
Starlink Airlines has gone bankrupt. After learning she&#039;s jobless, Claire has a serious panic attack - that is, until the phone rings. The new owner of Starlink Airlines wants to rebuild the business by hiring top talent. Claire might be a little rusty as a flight attendant - help her back into the groove by serving coffee promptly to passengers. Fly in First Class Flurry as a star attendant in this Time Management destination game.

    * Time-Management in the friendly skies
    * Become a flight attendant
    * Customize your planes
